    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032560/extras/b5e0ed0c23f2219d01d8fa69e15d0e3e.poster.avif?t=1722267781\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032560/extras/b5e0ed0c23f2219d01d8fa69e15d0e3e.webm?t=1722267781\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Jam Jump</strong> 是一款令人兴奋的动作平台游戏，背景设定在普尔诺特的神秘土地上。扮演一位年轻的骑士，展开一场激动人心的冒险，面对成群的敌人，并展示您的敏捷性，穿越分散的岛屿。游戏包含多样的敌人、激烈的boss战和引人入胜的谜题，将考验您的技能和策略。随着每个关卡的进行，挑战变得更加艰难，要求快速反应和聪明的问题解决。准备好在Jam Jump中跳跃、战斗和解决谜题，进行一次史诗般的旅程吧！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032560/extras/62937eda66dc9450696d2ae398b5eaca.poster.avif?t=1722267781\" width=598 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032560/extras/62937eda66dc9450696d2ae398b5eaca.webm?t=1722267781\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032560/extras/62937eda66dc9450696d2ae398b5eaca.mp4?t=1722267781\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>主要特点：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >动作充满的游戏玩法</h2></strong> 在穿越敌人的过程中体验快速的动作，利用各种战斗技能击败他们。<br></li><li><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >富有挑战性的跳跃平台</h2></strong> 在背叛性的岛屿和障碍中导航，需要精确的跳跃和灵活的动作来生存和前进。<br></li><li><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >激烈的boss战</h2></strong> 在每个阶段的末尾面对强大的boss，每个boss都提供独特的挑战，需要战略性战斗来克服。<br></li><li><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >引人入胜的谜题</h2></strong> 解决引人入胜的谜题，这些谜题与跳跃和战斗元素交织在一起，为游戏玩法增加了深度和多样性。<br></li><li><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >多样的环境</h2></strong> 探索美丽设计的关卡，这些关卡位于魔法土地的不同部分，每个部分都有自己独特的视觉风格和挑战。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032560/extras/4ac6b48d89be06fd51fb4d29984af800.poster.avif?t=1722267781\" width=600 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032560/extras/4ac6b48d89be06fd51fb4d29984af800.webm?t=1722267781\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032560/extras/4ac6b48d89be06fd51fb4d29984af800.mp4?t=1722267781\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
